   equiv fcs (Tie a1 t1) (Tie a2 t2)) ∧
  (equiv fcs t1a t2a ∧ equiv fcs t1d t2d ⇒
   equiv fcs (nPair t1a t1d) (nPair t2a t2d)) ∧
  (equiv fcs (nConst c) (nConst c))`

